thread.title: J Moh
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by J Moh

author: J Moh
title: J Moh
text: We've hired cars from omega before and have always found their prices reasonable and service great. This time was no different. We had to pick car up after hours and we were sent clear instructions on where the car is and location of key. It was a recent model of corolla which was immaculate. We thoroughly enjoyed driving it for the weekend.
